{"tid":1168441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十倍量刑　法官邪惡　黃之鋒案砌戴耀廷生豬　德國佬睇得通透","createTime":"2019-05-23T16:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:09:43.000Z","uid":47714,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"47b5217115a0783d95673fb8496dfa4ea3a63c81","tid":1168441,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330387603038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2426330387603038&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=cbfc5fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330387603038</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330990936311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2426330990936311&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=2b4cccb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330990936311</a><br />\n<br />\n十倍量刑額外步驟（aka 黃之鋒案）嘅問題，歐陸法學叫唔符合比例原則，普通法叫做唔合乎公眾期望加上fettering discretion。正統普通法嘅理解純粹係法官邪惡、legislate from the bench，但歐陸則睇得通透好多，德國佬一眼望落去就知道咩事。<br />\n<br />\n正統歐陸「比例原則」係用來分析黃之鋒案，唔係用來砌戴耀廷生豬肉。呢啲嘢德國佬當然熟過啲兩頭唔到岸嘅垃圾。"},{"pid":"676da371a43ed3f2f77808f01550d07e6d3aec07","tid":1168441,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47b5217115a0783d95673fb8496dfa4ea3a63c81","tid":1168441,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330387603038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2426330387603038&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=cbfc5fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330387603038</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2426330990936311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin